snippet.title: Obduction Teaser Trailer
snippet.description: Welcome to Obduction, Cyan's highly anticipated spiritual successor to Myst. This teaser trailer finally pulls back the curtain for a sneak peek of what to expect. Obduction is scheduled for release in August, 2016. (Spoiler alert for purists.)
